      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NATISA'S SECRET (2) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 22.18 beating Pitman Go Well. Has a low draw and goes well at this distance. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Can continue the winning form. SILENT MINUTE (8) goes very well here starting four times for two wins and two minors. Placed last time (18.99) at Richmond in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 9 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. NOVA LASS (3) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (23.36) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. Should play a prominent role. MISS MAXI (7) will have admirers again after placing at this track and distance last time out.",
